longBusinessSummary: eWellness Healthcare Corporation, a physical therapy telehealth company, offers real-time distance monitored assessments and treatments. It operates PHZIO, a real-time remote monitored 1-to-many musculoskeletal treatment physical therapy platform for home use. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Fort Lauderdale, Florida.
